
= Managing Director, Euro Freelancers, Brussels, Belgium

=Bio=

"OuiShare European Union Connector and founder at www.euro-freelancers.eu, a synergic network of independent EU affairs professionals and investors specialised in sustainability, collaborative innovation and crowd-sourcing solutions. As EU policy and legal advisor specialised in sustainable consumption and production, I am relentlessly building bridges between co-consumption and co-creation movements as a conduit to create skills, work, new forms of wealth and a resource efficient society. Having great passion for how the collaborative economy and peer-to-peer networks enable and disrupt markets and regulations, I thrive to be on the edge of EU policy and business" 


